title: 2020 CFB Pick Em Week 14
description:
El Pres, Big Cat and Rico Bosco are back for another week of picks. Tensions were high from the start when Rico referred to the podcast as his “whore session” There’s also a debate on the integrity of one college basketball podcast stealing march designs from their rival. The Pat Hill Trophy race remains tight heading into the weekend!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
